<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your DATLEP Password</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1e40af 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .otp-container {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .otp-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        .otp-expiry {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ef4444;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #1e40af 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .action-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.2);
        }

        .instructions {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .instructions h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .instructions ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .security-note {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .security-note h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .security-note p {
            color: #7f1d1d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .copyright {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .device-info {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .otp-code {
                font-size: 32px;
                letter-spacing: 6px;
            }

            .action-button {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">DATLEP</div>
            <div class="tagline">Craftsmanship Meets Technology</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Greeting -->
            <h1 class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
            
            <!-- Message -->
            <p class="message">
                We received a request to reset the password for your DATLEP account. 
                Use the OTP below to complete the password reset process.
            </p>

            <!-- OTP Section -->
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                <div class="otp-expiry">⚠️ Expires in 5 minutes</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Action Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="action-button">
                    Reset Password Now
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Instructions -->
            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>How to reset your password:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Enter the 6-digit OTP above on the password reset page</li>
                    <li>Create a new secure password</li>
                    <li>Confirm your new password</li>
                    <li>Click "Reset Password" to complete the process</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <!-- Security Note -->
            <div class="security-note">
                <h3>⚠️ Security Alert</h3>
                <p>
                    If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately. 
                    Never share your OTP with anyone. DATLEP will never ask for your password or OTP.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Additional Info -->
            <p class="message" style="font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>Note:</strong> This OTP is valid for 5 minutes only. After expiration, you'll need to request a new OTP.
                <br><br>
                For security reasons, please complete the password reset process on the same device you used to make this request.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? We're here for you!</p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="https://datlep.com/help">Help Center</a>
                <a href="https://datlep.com/contact">Contact Support</a>
                <a href="https://datlep.com/security">Security Tips</a>
            </div>
            <p class="copyright">
                © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> DATLEP. All rights reserved.<br>
                Craftsmanship, Convenience, and Technology.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Device Info -->
            <div class="device-info">
                This email was sent to <%= email %> from a password reset request.
                <br>
                If this wasn't you, please secure your account immediately.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>